title: Eps. 128 - Stop Complaining
description:
How many of you are in situations that you don’t like ? How many of you have circumstances that you aren’t in favor of ? On today’s podcast ET talks about individuals who don’t like where they are but who aren’t doing anything about it. There are things you can do to get better as a person, employee, and to get better in your craft. ET makes the claim that becoming better will give you the opportunity to have, be, and do what you want to do in life.
 Time Stamped Topics:
  [02:00] - Ring The Alarm
 [12:04] - What The Heck Was ET Trying To Say ?
 [23:36] - It’s A Bigger Issue
 [33:00] - Learn To Follow Through
 [49:00] - Becoming An Executor
 [1:00:00] - Full Execution
 [1:12:35] - Nugget Of The Day
 [1:20:35] - Fair or Foul
  Listener Perks:
  Organifi is giving our listeners 20% off of their order just use the promo code “SUCCESS”. Their superfood green juice powder allows you to get your greens anytime anywhere while on the go.
 Hello Fresh is giving our listeners $30 off your first week of deliveries just use the code “SUCCESS30”
  The Secrets To Success:
  “What are the things you have not done at this point that have not allowed you to be where you want to be ?”
 “What do I need to change to make myself better.”
 “The higher performer you are, the less crap you have to deal with.”
 “Everything you do should put you in a place to be something you aren’t.”
